Class Player

java.lang.Object
com.oniverse.neon_dystopia.model.utils.HitBox
com.oniverse.neon_dystopia.model.entities.Player
public class Player extends HitBox
Player : Class that represents the player in the game. It has a coordinate, a level and a health. It can move to a coordinate, and it can be damaged. It has a property change support to notify the level and the view when the player moves or gets damaged.
